children.text: • Designed and developed a dynamic, fully responsive personal portfolio using React, TypeScript, and Tailwind CSS, providing an engaging platform to showcase technical expertise and project accomplishments with seamless user experience across devices.
• Architected a cost-effective serverless infrastructure leveraging AWS services (S3, Lambda) to optimize content management processes, improve scalability, and reduce operational costs.
• Implemented Strapi as a headless CMS, seamlessly integrated with AWS EC2 for hosting, ensuring scalable content management and high-performance server operations.
• Developed a full-stack MERN application (MongoDB, Express.js, React, Node.js), independently managing front-end, back-end, and database layers.
• Designed an intuitive user interface using Adobe Photoshop and Figma, focusing on clean, user-friendly layouts and enhancing the overall user experience (UI/UX).
• Optimized back-end performance by mastering Express.js for efficient database operations and RESTful API integrations, improving communication between front-end and back-end components.
• Developed a cross-platform mobile app using React Native and Node.js to track and categorize daily expenses, with secure data storage handled through SQLite.
• Implemented an expense overview feature, displaying weekly expenses with real-time editing functionality for each entry.
